.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER_LOCAL_BALANCE_SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-local-balance-skewness \- FEAT-2813 skewness of local balance per peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-local-balance-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the skewness of local balance per peer for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2813).
.PP
Output: JSON object with key \fBlocal_balance_skewness_peer\fR and \fBcount\fR.
Returns \fBnull\fR when fewer than the required minimum samples are available.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning (1)
